<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1907/508273.jpg" alt="Mortimer Harvey wins Fidelity Services Group" width="150" height="150">Brands in the Fidelity Services Group stable are Fidelity ADT; Fidelity Fire Solutions; Fidelity Cleaning Services; Fidelity SecureDrive; Sensormatic; Fidelity Commercial and Cash in Transit (Cash Solutions).Andrew Fradd, Group Managing Director of MH, said, “The agency has welcomed the group into the MH family and look forward to ensuring the brand maintains its position as a front-runner in the security and protection solutions market.”